{"word":"κατοπτρίζω","slug":"κατοπτρίζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ϰατοπτρίζω</el></b> [<el>ϰάτοπτρον</el> ‘mirror’] <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ mid.\">mid.</a> <b>see reflected,</b> in imagery of looking at oneself in a mirror and seeing a face that reflects <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ someth.\">someth.</a> other than one’s customary visage, viz. <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:δόξα\">δόξα</a> ϰυρίου</el> <b><a href='B:540 3:18'>2 Cor 3:18</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:κατοικίζω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:κατόρθωμα\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}